00:00:18.250 --> 00:00:22.310
able to introduce Prof. Susan Crawford and
Chairman Tom Wheeler this afternoon. As I'm

00:00:22.310 --> 00:00:26.980
sure you know, Prof. Crawford teaches here
at HLS, works with us a lot in the Cyberlaw

00:00:26.980 --> 00:00:31.990
Clinic, and works a lot on issues related
to telecom as well as civic innovation, government

00:00:31.990 --> 00:00:38.170
innovation, and helping cities think through
data-smart governance and policies.

00:00:38.170 --> 00:00:43.290
